title: Grateful Dead Live at Providence Civic Center on 1981-05-13
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, Tennessee Jed, CC Rider, Friend Of The Devil, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Bird Song, Let It Grow-> Deal

Set 2

Samson & Delilah, Terrapin Station-> Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> Iko Iko-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Good Lovin', E: Brokedown Palace
